data.description: Newer construction in a highly sought-after location with NO ASSOCIATION AND NO CDD, the entire front of the home is pavered allowing plenty of parking without blocking any cars in. Single story home so no climbing or descending the stairs every time you forget something or need to go to the kitchen. The open floor plan makes the home look and feel extremely spacious making it ideal for entertaining or large family get-togethers  Kitchen features an island with sink and granite countertops. The home has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms but the seller has plans to convert the bedroom into a 5th bedroom which will be included in the sale.
